high_descs: go to the right of the stove
pick up the potato from the counter
take the potato to the microwave
cook the potato in the microwave then remove
take the cooked potato to the sink
put the potato in the sink
anns.task_desc: put a cooked potato in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and take a step then turn right and go to the counter to the right of the stove
Pick up the potato from the back of the counter
Turn around and take a step then turn left and go to the counter and face the microwave
Cook the potato in the microwave then take the potato out of the microwave
Turn around and take a step then turn right and go to the sink
Put the potato in the sink on the right
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato in a sink

high_descs: Make a left to walk towards the countertop directly to the right of the stove.
Pick up the potato sitting on the countertop to the right of the stove.
Turn around, then make a left to head towards the microwave.
Heat the potato to the right of the eggs in the microwave, removing it again.
Turn left to walk towards the sink.
Set the potato in the sink on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a potato in the microwave to put in the sink.
